flowchart TD
    A["NM Heartbeat arrives at RM"] --> B{"Does NM match requested Node Local?"}
    B -->|Yes| C["Allocate Node-Local Container"]
    B -->|No| D{"Does NM match requested Rack Local?"}
    D -->|Yes| E["Allocate Rack-Local Container"]
    D -->|No| F{"Is Rack-locality delay expired?"}
    F -->|Yes| G["Allocate Off-Switch / Any Container"]
    F -->|No| H["Skip allocation on this node, wait for next heartbeat"]
    C --> I["Acquire Container Token"]
    E --> I
    G --> I
    I --> J["Return Token in next AllocateResponse to AM"]
